306
00:18:39,165 --> 00:18:40,340
Hé! James!

307
00:18:40,668 --> 00:18:42,311
Edgar, wahou!

308
00:18:42,777 --> 00:18:43,761
Salut!

309
00:18:45,488 --> 00:18:46,473
Brillant!

310
00:18:47,305 --> 00:18:48,191
Jeremy!

311
00:18:49,318 --> 00:18:53,573
Comment ça se fait que tu connais
tous ces beaux jeunes hommes?

312
00:18:53,717 --> 00:18:55,033
Juste comme ça.

313
00:18:55,357 --> 00:18:58,242
Jerome! Viens là, mon grand!

314
00:18:59,767 --> 00:19:01,411
Salut, chéri.

